com.emc.vipr.client.core.util

Class CachedResources<T extends DataObjectRestRep>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.emc.vipr.client.core.util.CachedResources<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the resource type.

    public class CachedResources<T extends DataObjectRestRep>
extends java.lang.Object
    Wrapper around resources that can cache the results. This can be quite useful when looking up related resources from another type.

        public T get(java.net.URI id)
